
CREATED BY :Tal Tabak.

Description:
In this program we have one program that simulate simple Shell of Linux.
The shell supports all of the simple linuk shell commands and also supports pipe commands 
and redirection commands.  


Program files: 
shell.c - contains main and functions.
shell - run file.
makefile - to compile the program.

Compile and running: 
In Visual Studio code
To compile: Ctrl + shift + b 
To run: Ctrl + f5 

In Linnux terminal:
to compile : gcc ex2.c -o ex2
to run: ./ex2

Input: 
commands
pipe commands
redirection commands

Output:
output of the known commands, pipe and redirection commands. 
and sammary at the end.
